# Third-Party Licenses (Rust dependencies)

This file lists the licenses of Rust crates statically linked into
the Minerva Coach desktop app binary. It is regenerated automatically
from `Cargo.lock` on every build by `.github/workflows/licenses.yml`.

JavaScript dependency licenses are appended after this section under
"Third-Party Licenses (npm dependencies)".

